---
---
<section class="download" id="download">
  <div class="container download-grid">
    <div class="download-left">
      <span class="eyebrow-line">04 · Download</span>
      <h2 class="download-title">
        Windows only.<br/>No account. No email.
      </h2>
      <p class="download-sub">
        Installer is about 50 MB. Opens in under a second on a modern laptop.
      </p>
      <a href="#" class="cta-primary large">Download for Windows (Free Beta)</a>
      <div class="download-meta">v0.5.0 · Windows 10/11 · ~50 MB</div>
    </div>

    <aside class="callout">
      <div class="callout-badge-wrap">
        <div class="callout-badge">!</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="callout-label">Install Note · SmartScreen</div>
        <div class="callout-lead">Unsigned beta installer.</div>
        <div class="callout-body">
          Windows SmartScreen may show <code>"not commonly downloaded"</code> — click
          <code>More info</code> → <code>Run anyway</code>. Signed installers start with v1.1.
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .download {
    padding: clamp(72px, 10vw, 120px) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line-1);
    background: var(--bg-0);
  }
  .download-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .download-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 3.6vw, 42px);
    line-height: 1.06;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-1);
    margin: 18px 0 16px;
  }
  .download-sub {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--fg-3);
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    max-width: 440px;
  }
  .download-meta {
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-4);
  }
  .callout-badge-wrap {
    min-width: 44px;
  }
  .callout-badge {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line-3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--fg-2);
  }
  .callout-lead {
    color: var(--fg-1);
    font-size: 14.5px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .callout-body {
    color: var(--fg-3);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .download {
      padding: 56px 0 64px;
    }
    .download-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .download-title {
      font-size: 30px;
      margin: 14px 0 14px;
    }
    .download-sub {
      font-size: 15px;
    }
  }
</style>
